ZH: 品管是一种管理方式，旨在确保产品或服务的质量。
EN: Quality control is a management approach designed to ensure the quality of products or services.

ZH: 我们公司非常重视品管，以提供高质量的产品。
EN: Our company places great importance on quality control to deliver high-quality products.

ZH: 品管标准是制定一个产品应满足的要求。
EN: Quality control standards are established to define the requirements a product must meet.

ZH: 这个工序的品管出了点问题，导致了一批次的次品。
EN: There was an issue with the quality control of this process, resulting in a batch of defective products.

ZH: 品管流程包括检测、检验和纠正。
EN: The quality control process includes inspection, testing, and corrective actions.

ZH: 我们每天都进行品管检查，确保产品符合标准。
EN: We perform quality control checks every day to ensure the products meet the standards.

ZH: 这家工厂有一套严格的品管制度，以确保每个产品都是优质的。
EN: This factory has a strict quality control system in place to ensure that every product is of high quality.

ZH: 我们的品管团队负责监控生产线上的质量问题。
EN: Our quality control team is responsible for monitoring quality issues on the production line.

ZH: 在品管部门，我们注重纠正生产过程中的问题并防止再次出现。
EN: In the quality control department, we focus on correcting production process issues and preventing their recurrence.

ZH: 品管部门会定期进行内部审核，以确保系统的有效性。
EN: The quality control department conducts regular internal audits to ensure the effectiveness of the system.

ZH: 我们与供应商合作，共同建立品管控制措施。
EN: We collaborate with suppliers to establish quality control measures.

ZH: 品管报告提供了产品质量的详细分析和评估。
EN: The quality control report provides a detailed analysis and evaluation of product quality.

ZH: 这名员工因为疏忽大意导致了一次品管失误。
EN: This employee caused a quality control error due to negligence.

ZH: 我们的目标是实现零次品，不断提高品管水平。
EN: Our goal is to achieve zero defects and continuously improve our quality control level.

ZH: 品管部门对于产品问题的处理非常及时和全面。
EN: The quality control department handles product issues in a timely and comprehensive manner.

ZH: 此次生产的问题需要品管部门进行深入调查。
EN: The issues in this production require a thorough investigation by the quality control department.

ZH: 在品管过程中，我们要遵循标准操作程序。
EN: During the quality control process, we must follow standard operating procedures.

ZH: 仪器维护是品管的重要一环，以确保准确性和可靠性。
EN: Equipment maintenance is an important part of quality control to ensure accuracy and reliability.

ZH: 我们需要建立一个更严密的品管体系来解决这些质量问题。
EN: We need to establish a more rigorous quality control system to address these quality issues.

ZH: 品管不仅仅是一项任务，而是一种质量意识的体现。
EN: Quality control is not just a task; it is an embodiment of quality consciousness.
